				</div>
				<div class="scroll-indicator">
					<span>Scroll</span>
					<svg
						width="24"
						height="24"
						viewBox="0 0 24 24"
						fill="none"
						stroke="currentColor"
						stroke-width="2"
					>
						<polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
					</svg>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
		<!-- What We Do -->
		<section class="section">
			<div class="container">
				<h2 class="section-title">What We Do</h2>
				<div class="content-card">
					<p>
						Starlit Customs specializes in <strong
							>fibre-optic starlight headliner installations</strong
						> for automotive interiors. We install high-quality custom
						starlight kits, designed and laid out specifically for each
						vehicle.
					</p>
					<p>
						Every headliner is stripped, marked, and rebuilt by hand
						to achieve even illumination, clean routing, and a
						factory-level finish that looks intentional, not
						aftermarket.
					</p>
					<p class="highlight">
						This is not a pre-made insert or a rushed job. Each
						install is tailored to the car, the interior, and the
						vision of the owner.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
		<!-- Why Choose Us -->
		<section class="section section-dark">
			<div class="container">
				<h2 class="section-title">Why Choose Starlit Customs</h2>
